title: Take a Wok
typeOfFood: Ovo, Thai, Beer/Wine, Asian, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Asian fusion restaurant and bar. The menu consists of 4 steps, whereas number 2 and 4 are optional. Choosing a base, a protein (has tofu), sauce, and then toppings. The vegetarian "eggrolls" are vegan.
venueHours: Mon-Tue 4:00pm-10:00pm, Wed-Thu 6:00pm-10:00pm, Wed-Fri 12:00pm-3:00pm, Fri 6:00pm-11:00pm, Sat 12:00pm-11:00pm, Sun 12:00pm-10:00pm
